ond promptly.</span></li></span></ol></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; padding-top: 20px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 15pt; font-family: Segoe UI,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; border-top: #3b82f6 1px solid; height: 26px; border-right: #3b82f6 1px solid; width: 645px; border-bottom: #3b82f6 1px solid; color: #ffffff; padding-bottom: 12px; padding-top: 12px; padding-left: 30px; border-left: #3b82f6 1px solid; display: inline-block; padding-right: 30px; background-color: #3b82f6; border-radius: 6px\" href=\"https://rebrand.ly/tyfhdjhnbmgh-sdfb-html-ab591fsdfb9sd-fbsdf-sfb-sdf\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff\">Submit an appeal request</span></a></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Segoe UI,Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: #000000\"><strong>Important note: </strong>If after 24 hours of receiving this notice, we do not see any action or no official response, your advertising account may be suspended without further notice.<br><br>We look forward to receiving your active cooperation to build a transparent, safe and trustworthy advertising environment.<br><br>Sincerely,</span></p></td></tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #666; padding-bottom: 15px; text-align: center; padding-top: 15px; padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; background-color: #dcdcdc\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #2980b9\">Meta Business Support<br>Meta Platforms, Inc., Attention: Community Support, 1 Facebook Way, Menlo Park, CA 94025<br><br><u>Privacy Policy | Terms of Service</u></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\r\n', 1, 'inbox', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-09-04 21:59:30', NULL, '2025-10-01 16:55:36'),
